OL,3,CCardiff City manager Erol Bulut sacked
OL,5,FCardiff City manager Erol Bulut has
OL,6,Fbeen sacked, the football club has
OL,7,Fconfirmed.
OL,9,FThe Bluebirds are at the bottom of the
OL,10,FChampionship, with Bulut's final game
OL,11,Fon Saturday seeing Leeds United defeat
OL,12,FCardiff 2-0.
OL,14,FThe Bluebirds have also lost to
OL,15,FSunderland, Burnley, Middlesbrough and
OL,16,FDerby County. Their only point came in
OL,17,Fthe south Wales derby against Swansea
OL,18,FCity.
