OL,3,CCardiff City manager Erol Bulut sacked
OL,5,FA statement posted on Cardiff City's
OL,6,Fwebsite on Sunday confirmed that Bulut
OL,7,Fhad been "relieved of his duties" and
OL,8,Fthat he "will leave the Club with
OL,9,Fimmediate effect."
OL,11,FThe statement continued: "The Board of
OL,12,FDirectors wish to thank Erol for all
OL,13,Fof his hard work and wish him well for
OL,14,Fthe future.
OL,16,F"First Team Coach Nikolaos Karydas
OL,17,Fwill also depart and leaves with the
OL,18,FClub's best wishes. Further backroom
OL,19,Fstaff confirmation will follow in due
OL,20,Fcourse.
